    "end": 490.8599853515625,
    "text": "our events and programs. So looking at how do we define our events first, how do we figure out the levels of the events, and then how do we build a framework around this? So to rewind back a little bit, we have a lot of events and programming with the city. We have a very robust schedule within the Department of Parks and Rec between special events and our cultural arts programming and everything else that we're doing. So we look at programming as something that's occurring regularly. These are small items, usually things like the community cleanups, the old town hall"
