    "text": "One of our biggest challenges right now is that we continue to be approached by people who would like to host events within the city, because they've heard about this great deal that a number of people are getting, and they would like to know how to get this deal as well. And so one of our challenges is really how we say yes or no to that and be equitable in that. We want to offset the long-term impact on city resources and support sustainable event management, because along with these third-party events, we have a lot of events within the city that we're already doing."
