    "text": "I think one of the things to keep in mind is that we want to create some framework. So we struggle with saying that we prefer an option, but I've heard the analogy used before, playing without any boundaries or guardrails or without a tennis net, so to speak. That's what we're doing right now. So fundamentally, we need to get to a point where we have an approach and a program that Council is aware of, understands, and signed off on. It could align very well to a budget year. We could decide that we have different tiers"
